WEBVTT

00:00:06.454 --> 00:00:08.871
Welcome to It Hurts!

00:00:09.329 --> 00:00:11.538
One of these creatures is thought 
to possess

00:00:11.538 --> 00:00:14.496
the world’s most painful insect sting.

00:00:15.204 --> 00:00:17.788
If you were to guess, would it be:

00:00:17.788 --> 00:00:21.121
the ant that forages 
in rainforest canopies?

00:00:21.121 --> 00:00:24.454
The bee that protects a hive
of delectable honey?

00:00:24.454 --> 00:00:28.079
Or the wasp that paralyzes tarantulas?

00:00:29.079 --> 00:00:31.038
Let’s find out!